title: All Beatles Songbooks (2nd attempt)
description:
(Second attempt - removed duplicates and non-songbook files)

Inspired by the recent "1000 piano song books" torrent (Thank you to the original poster!). Here is my collection of easy to intermediate Beatles song books for piano, guitar and voice (along with a one biographical book describing their most popular songs).  

Files:

Beatlemania 1963-1966 vol 1
Beatles 100 Hits for All Keyboards
Beatles - Easy piano
Beatles - It's Easy To Play Beatles. Vol 1 For PVG (Arr. by Daniel Scott) vol. 01
Beatles - It's Easy To Play Beatles. Vol 2 For PVG (Arr. by Daniel Scott) vol. 02
Beatles - Live at the Hollywood Bowl -PVG
Beatles - Songbook Piano 1962-1974
Beatles - Songs and Comments. Vol. 02 (Arr. unknown)
Beatles - Songs for voice with piano-guitar. Vol. 01
Beatles - Songs for voice with piano-guitar. Vol. 02
Beatles - Songs of Liverpoodlinan Four (Arr. unknown)
Beatles - Translations For Piano (arr. Alexandr Gavrilov)
Beatles for Jazz Piano
Beatles Medley love is all you need - hal leonard
Its Easy To Play Beatles
John Lennon - Just like starting over-PVG
Play Piano With the Beatles
The Beatles-Yeah Yeah Yeah songbook

Please seed this torrent if you like it!


If you have other Beatles songbooks I have missed, please consider sharing.
